In order to properly project the 3D figure, you need to change the terminal size to be equal (for example &#039;350,350&#039;), and to add the following:
&lt;pre class=&quot;prettyprint&quot;&gt;
set view equal xyz
set xyplane relative 0.0
&lt;/pre&gt;
